Package: CardioRVAR
Type: Package
Title: Spectral Analysis of Open and Closed-Loop Cardiovascular Interactions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alvaro Chao-Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com> [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2691-6936>), 
        Marc Stefan Dawid-Milner [aut]
Maintainer: Alvaro Chao Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com>
Description: This is an R package designed for modelling cardiovascular open-
             and closed-loop interactions. It is advisable that this package 
             is used with the separate ShinyApp interface, CarioRVARapp,
             for a better user-friendly experience.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/CIMES-USNA-UMA/CardioRVAR
BugReports: https://github.com/CIMES-USNA-UMA/CardioRVAR/issues
